                    <a href="/debates/?id=1961-03-22a.413.0" class="link debate-speech__meta__link">Individually</a>
                </li>
                                <li class="link-to-speech">
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theyworkforyou.com%2Fdebates%2F%3Fid%3D1961-03-22a.413.0&amp;text=Orders+of+the+Day+%26%238212%3B+Sierra+Leone+Independence+Bill+on+TheyWorkForYou&amp;amp;related=theyworkforyou%2Cmysociety" class="twitter debate-speech__meta__link js-twitter-share" target="_blank">Tweet</a>
